Rating: 4
I'm surprised by the poor reviews for this recipe. My husband and I really liked it -- the grated Parmesan cheese created a lovely coating on each strand of linguine. I reviewed this recipe on my own blog, Recipes That Worked by Mandy Higgins.

Rating: 2
I was not impressed by this recipe. I followed some of the suggestions, and was still not pleased with the turnout. It lacked any zest in the flavor, but showcased the vegetables nicely. I don't think I'll be making this recipe again unfortunately.

